---
title: Crumbed Halloumi & Chicken Burger with Caramelised Onions & Kūmara Fries
description: Serve up a hearty burger with this version made with a golden "patty" of crumbed halloumi & chicken! A smear of smokey aioli and sweet
caramelised onion turns this veggie dinner into a taste sensation.

